## Bug Borg type information

borg-type-generic_bug-name = Generic
borg-type-generic_bug-desc = Jack of all trades, master of none. Do various random station tasks, or maybe help out the science department that built you.
borg-type-generic_bug-transponder = generic cyborg

borg-type-engineering_bug-name = Engineering
borg-type-engineering_bug-desc = Assist the engineering team in station construction, repairing damage, or fixing electrical and atmospheric issues.
borg-type-engineering_bug-transponder = engineering cyborg

borg-type-mining_bug-name = Salvage
borg-type-mining_bug-desc = Join salvage and help them mine for materials, scavenge wrecks, and fight off hostile wildlife.
borg-type-mining_bug-transponder = salvage cyborg

borg-type-janitor_bug-name = Janitor
borg-type-janitor_bug-desc = Keep the station nice and tidy, clean up spills, collect and properly dispose of trash left around by lazy crewmembers.
borg-type-janitor_bug-transponder = janitor cyborg

borg-type-medical_bug-name = Medical
borg-type-medical_bug-desc = Provide medical attention to crew who need it, either in medbay or in hazardous areas conventional paramedics cannot reach.
borg-type-medical_bug-transponder = medical cyborg

borg-type-service_bug-name = Service
borg-type-service_bug-desc = Help out with a wide range of crew services, ranging from serving snacks and drinks to botany to entertainment.
borg-type-service_bug-transponder = service cyborg